    "created_at": "2012-06-29T19:50:50Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-06-29T19:50:50Z",
    "body": "Just to elaborate, \"pure\" means \"as pure as the borrow check needs a pure function to be\"... which is a weaker notion than referential transparency, and isn't the same kind of \"pure\" that typestate would want either.\n",
