    "created_at": "2012-11-24T17:50:27Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-11-24T17:50:27Z",
    "body": "There doesn't seem to be much interest in changing the keyword, and now that we no longer have typestate we no longer have the motivating reason that there are two notions of purity. So I'm closing.\n",
